{"tid":2051704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：不應只撤離祿泉樓10及12號住戶","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:42:53.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a898d3d49725414c0043e598ab858482e77d858c","tid":2051704,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"何栢良：不應只撤離祿泉樓10及12號住戶<br />\n2020-06-05 HKT 11:21<br />\n<br />\n香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，暫時未有明顯證據顯示沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓的病毒傳播途徑，最先出現感染個案的8樓，已有3個單位有人確診，證明有一定風險，因此認為當局不應該只撤離10及12號單位的住戶，8樓全層的住戶亦應該送到檢疫中心接受觀察。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良又以2003年沙士、淘大花園的經驗為例，指病毒傳播有3種可能性，包括透過公共環境、U型渠或排氣喉、以及氣流傳播，指如果有居民咳嗽，飛沫有可能隨氣流傳到鄰近的單位或走廊。<br />\n<br />\n據他了解，祿泉樓仍有6戶居民未能聯絡上，何栢良建議當局應要求警方協助尋找這些住戶。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530321-20200605.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530321-20200605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=21ce4a29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530321-20200605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=46aea78d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530321-20200605.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4bda8c4cee1e47f143501e0bdfda351eff51a2c3","tid":2051704,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"撤離全香港最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc912dd4014cbbc85d7256e688baa707c62d0fb4","tid":2051704,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"成條村好冇"},{"pid":"621da8ee15f2be9dbb5d758ed498314f7aea9771","tid":2051704,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:41:13.000Z","msg":"專家全部恐懼撚黎<br />\n燈撚走晒D 病毒<br />\n睇死咪又連續幾日0本地確診"},{"pid":"6e1db50c0c665aa817cbc376a5b36e130a20ea57","tid":2051704,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:42:53.000Z","msg":"政府已經唔聽你支笛喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}